{"tid":2507461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"崇日能是站著喝酒而穿動漫Tee的唯一的人","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T04:48:31.000Z","uid":117802,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdee48da0aeebd056ba702bdbbe8eaa6653f6ff","tid":2507461,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"崇日能是站著喝酒而穿動漫Tee的唯一的人。他身材很矮小；青白臉色，皺紋間時常夾些暗瘡；一部亂蓬蓬的花白的鬍子。穿的雖然是長衫，可是又髒又破，似乎十多年沒有補，也沒有洗。他對人說話，總是滿口日文單詞，教人半懂不懂的。<br />\n<br />\n因為他盲撐日本又盲反韓國，別人便替他取下一個綽號，叫作崇日能。崇日能一到娛台，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「崇日能，宣布泡菜文化正式收工未啊？」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「唔鎖國，Arashi紅遍亞洲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「十年過咗，日本再度將音樂娛樂呢塊版圖拎返嚟未啊？」崇日能睜大眼睛說，「真係覺得完全<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔撚明</span></span>d小朋友鍾意佢地d咩」<br />\n「<em>青瓦台國民請願要求停播朝鮮驅魔師，廣告商割蓆，對抗中國文化入侵；秋葉原AKB48劇場廣告板被《原神》取代⋯⋯</em>」崇日能便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「反韓不能算&hellip;&hellip;盲反！大和文化精神，能算盲反麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「00後有冇聽過黑澤明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，什麼「死泡狗又整容，日本明星女大十八變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來：娛台內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"eabd11ebd246d48cc4d5caafb77bc59b249151b6","tid":2507461,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a8e1877a89b86445ac104c6c3b9cdedc1bd365","tid":2507461,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eabd11ebd246d48cc4d5caafb77bc59b249151b6","tid":2507461,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"如今既韓國係咪得返samsung可以仲講得出口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5359c534cef246cc0443d600e179214af69a57dc","tid":2507461,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430052d5648dda7c0387928995f1eb0b3e14561a","tid":2507461,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"死泡狗又陰d陰d反日..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61863c9db104fd3a561f380b268a3abc8e08f252","tid":2507461,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5359c534cef246cc0443d600e179214af69a57dc","tid":2507461,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"大家長大了"},{"pid":"12eb58dc0954ff176babf7fcbc475bf8992a0e41","tid":2507461,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430052d5648dda7c0387928995f1eb0b3e14561a","tid":2507461,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"死泡狗又陰d陰d反日..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"以個人預測這一波韓國浪潮大概撐不到幾年就走下坡了，因為日本就算這幾年比較沒落、但基礎打的深又好，還是有機會再度把亞洲音樂娛樂這一塊版圖給拿回來，韓國利用的是包裝還有訓練的力量，在音樂上還是略顯不足，我不看好韓國的原因就是這樣，其實對韓國人我不喜歡也不討厭。"},{"pid":"6c5f025c36ac4b7f22afcf16ba792a4ca28e89ca","tid":2507461,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"塊面又膠又醜 成個雞款 你睇埋我個份"},{"pid":"4ed7391dd262009db2aabd25955b32d63e9a935f","tid":2507461,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":